<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Aguarda Aprovação - Marketplace</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/admin.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/sidebar-supermarket') %>

    <main class="main-wrapper d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="min-height: 100vh;">
        <div class="text-center" style="max-width: 480px;">
            <i class="bi bi-hourglass-split text-warning" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mt-3 mb-2">A aguardar aprovação</h4>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                O teu registo foi recebido. A equipa de administração irá analisar e aprovar a tua loja em breve.
            </p>
            <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark fs-6 mb-4">
                <i class="bi bi-clock me-1"></i> Pendente
            </span>
            <div class="d-grid">
                <a href="/supermarket/settings" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-gear me-2"></i>Editar Perfil
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
